{
  "texts": [
    "Including artificial intelligence (AI) with Internet of Things (IoT) devices can also give real-time tracking and automatic compliance verifying, thus simplifying end-to-end logistical processes.",
    "The sector will move toward totally automated, data-driven supply chains as logistics companies keep employing AIpowered solutions.",
    "Companies implementing new degrees of efficiency, accuracy, and cost-effectiveness will be positioned for long-term success in an environment getting more and more digital and competitive."
  ]
}